    <p class="font-serif text-3xl text-ivory leading-relaxed mb-8">
      The web was a graph, and PageRank read it. A knowledge graph is
      a graph, and personalised PageRank reads it. Whatever comes next
      will also be a graph, because nearly everything is.
    </p>
    <p class="text-ivory-dim text-base mt-8 leading-relaxed">
      Graph theory began as a question about seven bridges in a city
      that no longer exists. It is now, in the most literal sense, the
      invisible mathematics of the age.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

